# SceneView MCP Pro Configuration
#
# Get your API key at https://polar.sh/sceneview
# After subscribing to SceneView MCP Pro (€9.99/mo), you'll receive an API key.

# Your SceneView MCP Pro API key (Stripe subscription ID)
# Set this to unlock Pro tools
# SCENEVIEW_API_KEY=sub_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Stripe secret key (server-side only — NEVER commit this!)
# Required for API key validation in production
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# For development/testing, leave STRIPE_SECRET_KEY unset
# and use SCENEVIEW_API_KEY=dev_test_key for local testing
